WEBVTT

00:09.840 --> 00:10.800
CHAPTER VIII.

00:10.940 --> 00:12.500
THINKING IN THE CERTAIN WAY

00:13.220 --> 00:17.580
Turn back to chapter 6, and read again the story of the man who formed the mental image

00:17.580 --> 00:21.940
of his house, and you will get a fair idea of the initial step toward getting rich.

00:22.260 --> 00:25.720
You must form a clear and definite mental picture of what you want.

00:26.060 --> 00:29.000
You cannot transmit an idea unless you have it yourself.

00:29.000 --> 00:31.880
You must have it before you can give it.

00:32.180 --> 00:37.100
A many people fail to impress thinking substance because they have themselves only a vague

00:37.100 --> 00:40.880
and mystic concept of the things they want to do, to have, or to become.

00:41.560 --> 00:45.900
It is not enough that you should have a general desire for wealth, to do, good with.

00:46.340 --> 00:47.820
Everybody has that desire.

00:48.460 --> 00:53.100
It is not enough that you should have a wish to travel, see things, live more, etc.

00:53.800 --> 00:55.920
Everybody has those desires also.

00:55.920 --> 01:00.860
If you are going to send a wireless message to a friend, you would not send the letters

01:00.860 --> 01:05.720
of the alphabet in their order and let him construct the message for himself, nor would

01:05.720 --> 01:07.880
you take words at random from the dictionary.

01:08.440 --> 01:11.860
You would send a coherent sentence, one which meant something.

01:12.680 --> 01:17.780
When you try to impress your wants upon substance, remember that it must be done by a coherent

01:17.780 --> 01:18.360
statement.

01:18.740 --> 01:20.980
You must know what you want and be definite.

01:21.400 --> 01:26.800
You can never get rich or start a creative power into action by sending out unformed

01:26.800 --> 01:28.540
longings and vague desires.

01:29.560 --> 01:34.260
Go over your desires just as the man I have described went over his house.

01:34.820 --> 01:39.380
See just what you want and get a clear mental picture of it as you wish it to look when

01:39.380 --> 01:40.060
you get it.

01:40.740 --> 01:46.140
That clear mental picture you must have continually in mind, as the sailor has in mind a port

01:46.140 --> 01:47.880
toward which he is sailing the ship.

01:48.240 --> 01:50.760
You must keep your face toward it all the time.

01:51.080 --> 01:55.500
You must no more lose sight of it than the steersman loses sight of the compass.

01:56.140 --> 02:02.400
It is not necessary to take exercises in concentration, nor to set apart special times for prayer

02:02.400 --> 02:08.040
and affirmation, nor to go into the silence, nor to do a cold stunt of any kind.

02:08.600 --> 02:13.260
These things are well enough, but all you need is to know what you want and to want

02:13.260 --> 02:16.100
it badly enough so that it will stay in your thoughts.

02:16.740 --> 02:21.540
Spend as much your leisure time as you can in contemplating your picture, but no one

02:21.540 --> 02:25.620
needs to take exercises to concentrate his mind on a thing he really wants.

02:26.200 --> 02:30.300
It is the things you do not really care about which require effort to fix your attention

02:30.300 --> 02:31.000
upon them.

02:31.600 --> 02:36.020
And unless you really want to get rich, so that the desire is strong enough to hold your

02:36.020 --> 02:41.300
thoughts directed to the purpose as the magnetic pole holds the needle of the compass, it will

02:41.300 --> 02:45.900
hardly be worthwhile for you to try to carry out the instructions given in this book.

02:46.440 --> 02:51.320
The methods herein set forth are for people whose desire for riches is strong enough to

02:51.320 --> 02:54.900
overcome mental laziness and a love of ease, and make them work.

02:55.760 --> 02:59.640
The more clear and definite you make your picture, then, and the more you dwell upon

02:59.640 --> 03:04.580
it, bringing out all its delightful details, the stronger your desire will be.

03:04.900 --> 03:09.620
And the stronger your desire, the easier it will be to hold your mind fixed upon the picture

03:09.620 --> 03:10.580
of what you want.

03:11.520 --> 03:15.320
Something more is necessary, however, than merely to see the picture clearly.

03:15.920 --> 03:21.680
If that is all you do, you are only a dreamer, and will have little or no power for accomplishment.

03:22.360 --> 03:27.220
Behind your clear vision must be the purpose to realize it, to bring it out in tangible

03:27.620 --> 03:27.880
expression.

03:28.500 --> 03:33.580
And behind this purpose must be an invincible and unwavering faith that the thing is already

03:33.580 --> 03:37.960
yours, that it is at hand, and you have only to take possession of it.

03:38.520 --> 03:42.580
Live in the new house mentally, until it takes form around you physically.

03:43.260 --> 03:47.380
In the mental realm, enter at once into full enjoyment of the things you want.

03:48.320 --> 03:53.240
Whatsoever things ye ask for when ye pray, believe that ye receive them, and ye shall

03:53.240 --> 03:54.900
have them, said Jesus.

03:55.840 --> 03:59.780
See the things you want as if they were actually around you all the time.

04:00.080 --> 04:02.420
See yourself as owning and using them.

04:02.930 --> 04:07.080
Make use of them in imagination, just as you will use them when they are your tangible

04:07.080 --> 04:07.800
possessions.

04:08.460 --> 04:12.860
Dwell upon your mental picture until it is clear and distinct, and then take the mental

04:12.860 --> 04:15.720
attitude of ownership toward everything in that picture.

04:16.220 --> 04:20.500
Take possession of it, in mind, in the full faith that it is actually yours.

04:21.160 --> 04:22.680
Hold to this mental ownership.

04:23.080 --> 04:26.220
Do not waver for an instant in the faith that it is real.

04:26.820 --> 04:30.220
And remember what was said in the preceding chapter about gratitude.

04:30.220 --> 04:35.500
Be as thankful for it all the time as you expect it to be when it has taken form.

04:35.980 --> 04:40.800
The man who can sincerely thank God for the things which as yet he owns only in imagination,

04:41.240 --> 04:42.060
has real faith.

04:42.680 --> 04:43.760
He will get rich.

04:44.000 --> 04:46.760
He will cause the creation of whatsoever he wants.

04:47.640 --> 04:50.340
You do not need to pray repeatedly for things you want.

04:50.640 --> 04:53.280
It is not necessary to tell God about it every day.

04:53.900 --> 04:59.580
Use not vain repetitions as the heathen do, said Jesus to his pupils, for your father

04:59.580 --> 05:03.000
knoweth that ye have need of these things before ye ask him.

05:03.500 --> 05:07.940
Your part is to intelligently formulate your desire for the things which make for a larger

05:07.940 --> 05:13.620
life, and to get these desires arranged into a coherent whole, and then to impress this

05:13.620 --> 05:18.120
whole desire upon the formless substance, which has the power and the will to bring

05:18.120 --> 05:19.020
you what you want.

05:19.880 --> 05:23.180
You do not make this impression by repeating strings of words.

05:23.460 --> 05:28.840
You make it by holding the vision with unshakable purpose to attain it, and with steadfast faith

05:28.840 --> 05:30.260
that you do attain it.

05:30.860 --> 05:35.320
The answer to prayer is not according to your faith while you are talking, but according

05:35.320 --> 05:37.140
to your faith while you are working.

05:37.700 --> 05:42.200
You cannot impress the mind of God by having a special Sabbath day set apart to tell him

05:42.200 --> 05:45.520
what you want, and of forgetting him during the rest of the week.

05:45.920 --> 05:50.780
You cannot impress him by having special hours to go into your closet and pray, if you then

05:50.780 --> 05:54.360
dismiss the matter from your mind until the hour of prayer comes again.

05:55.000 --> 06:00.680
Oral prayer is well enough, and has its effect, especially upon yourself, in clarifying your

06:00.680 --> 06:02.360
vision and strengthening your faith.

06:02.980 --> 06:06.120
But it is not your oral petitions which get you what you want.

06:07.080 --> 06:10.380
In order to get rich, you do not need a sweet hour of prayer.

06:10.740 --> 06:12.360
You need to pray without ceasing.

06:12.940 --> 06:17.580
And by prayer, I mean holding steadily to your vision, with the purpose to cause its

06:17.580 --> 06:21.360
creation into solid form, and the faith that you are doing so.

06:21.960 --> 06:23.620
Believe that ye receive them.

06:24.220 --> 06:28.240
The whole matter turns on receiving, once you have clearly formed your vision.

06:28.880 --> 06:33.440
When you have formed it, it is well to make an oral statement, addressing the supreme

06:33.440 --> 06:38.780
irreverent prayer, and from that moment you must, in mind, receive what you ask for.

06:39.420 --> 06:45.000
Live in the new house, wear the fine clothes, ride in the automobile, go on the journey,

06:45.300 --> 06:47.520
and confidently plan for greater journeys.

06:48.220 --> 06:52.720
Think and speak of all the things you have asked for in terms of actual present ownership.

06:53.260 --> 06:58.140
Imagine an environment and a financial condition exactly as you want them, and live all the

06:58.140 --> 07:01.300
time in that imaginary environment and financial condition.

07:01.880 --> 07:06.360
Mind, however, that you do not do this as a mere dreamer or castle-builder.

07:06.780 --> 07:11.660
Hold to the faith that the imaginary is being realized, and to the purpose to realize it.

07:12.160 --> 07:16.860
Remember that it is faith and purpose in the use of the imagination which makes the difference

07:16.860 --> 07:18.960
between the scientist and the dreamer.

07:19.280 --> 07:23.900
And having learned this fact, it is here that you must learn the proper use of the will.

07:25.380 --> 07:26.460
End of chapter 8

